Titolo: The Attack of the Phantom Karate Devils

Anno: 1983

Descrizione: The Attack of the Phantom Karate Devils is a video game developed by John Orthel for Phantom Software on the Commodore 64 in  1983.  The game play involves a side view of the character that would be reminiscent of modern fighting games.  Using a joystick the player can move and perform various attacks fighting their way through 4 stages.